T1  - Validating the Halp Score (Hemoglobin,Albumin, Lymphocytes, and Platelets) and the Neutrophil/Lymphocyte Ratio ( NLR) As Prognostic Factors for Overall Survival in Patients with Diffuse Large B-Cell Lymphoma. Retrospective Analysis By the Grupo De Estudio De Latino America De Linfoproliferativos (GELL)
