N2  - The intestinal parasitosis is a world health problem. The countries which don't have any economic, sanitary or educational resources are the most affected. Perú doesn't scape of that situation and for this reason, it is necessary that health professionals should have clinical therapeutical and epidemiological acknowledgements in order to be applied efficiently in benefit of the community. This paper there is a review of newer treatment of the enteroparasitosis, regarding the classic drugs and the ones which have been recently introduced.
